name				FreeDroid RPG
headline			Game inpired by Paradroid on the Commodore 64
description
	Freedroid exists in two flavors: - FreedroidClassic is a 2D arcade game similar to Paradroid - FreedroidRPG is an original isometric 3D role playing game inspired from Diablo and Fallout, taking place in the future, on Earth.
	This is a clone of the classic game "Paradroid" on Commodore 64 with some improvements and extensions to the original version.
